{"tid":2262034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警會面室設投影系統即場拍手機內容 毋須將數碼裝置交到網罪科檢驗","createTime":"2020-10-28T19:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd6e538210eed879a15c3f455c4d91f0da00258","tid":2262034,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"「反送中」運動期間，不少抗爭者都被警方要求解鎖手機，部份手機更遭警方破解。警隊網絡安全及科技罪案調查科於今年9月起開展先導計劃，在部份警署的錄影會面室內安裝實物投影支援系統，即場拍下手機內容，以更快向會面人士提問和作為日後審訊的證物，手機亦毋須交到網罪科檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n大律師石書銘表示，警方如要開啟手機，需要當事人自願提供密碼，或由法庭申請搜查令，再透過軟件破解。他相信，只在當事人沒有在手機設定密碼，或當事人自願提供密碼予警方，警方才能夠使用新系統拍下手機內容。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，被捕人士如在警方引誘或威嚇下，終向警方提供手機密碼，警方所得的證據也可用作指證被捕人士本人。他曾聽聞警員得到手機密碼後，隨即自行拍攝手機內容，但用新系統獲取資料則首次聽聞，相信可令警方在調查和行政上更便利。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，被捕人士有權不向警方提供密碼，而即使主動為手機解鎖，警方亦不會發還手機予當事人，「你合作嘅話，只會令佢哋更易攞到資料。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/NZJCX2ILWRFF3N5SPMXMXCK6QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FNZJCX2ILWRFF3N5SPMXMXCK6QA%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kim5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=bb76fa93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FNZJCX2ILWRFF3N5SPMXMXCK6QA%2F&h=cd7ddba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/NZJCX2ILWRFF3N5SPMXMXCK6QA/</a>"},{"pid":"202343fdca95aae1e493216fbed1b07d39a09373","tid":2262034,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"分化了"},{"pid":"baf703741be2fe1a05b4b588738a71b8ad51c2df","tid":2262034,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:18:21.000Z","msg":"以後出街唔撚帶手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea771df38f118c427cc6d3929f3c672da575d907","tid":2262034,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:19:22.000Z","msg":"好撚抑鬱 而家仲有冇手足係連登入面陪我發神經?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2261589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2261589</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c14884220234a8ebbe3c2ae10e703dcc5e8b56e","tid":2262034,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">一早話大律師公會專出賤人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大律師石書銘表示</strong>，警方如要開啟手機，需要當事人自願提供密碼，或由法庭申請搜查令，再透過軟件破解<strong>。他相信，只在當事人沒有在手機設定密碼，或當事人自願提供密碼予警方，警方才能夠使用新系統拍下手機內容。</strong>"},{"pid":"29582cb7f2a2b087269849f83b59ee9b9d2684ee","tid":2262034,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:22:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E9%81%8E%E9%87%8D-%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%BB%A3-%E5%89%96%E9%87%8B%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2587%258D-%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25BB%25A3-%25E5%2589%2596%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kim5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=690b88e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2587%258D-%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25BB%25A3-%25E5%2589%2596%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=65b8ac45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E9%81%8E%E9%87%8D-%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%BB%A3-%E5%89%96%E9%87%8B%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n執業大律師、公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋則稱，理解今次官司會令社會產生憂慮，但認為未必需要過慮，若被告上訴，上訴庭或可進一步釐清「破壞社會安寧」的定義。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次判決，是否令日後的社會運動風險增加？楊岳橋指，若示威者秉持和平精神，相信影響不大。楊岳橋指，任何牽涉暴力的行為，警方都有可能以「暴動」起訴，但相信法院理性，不會將任何超出和平的示威都等同暴動。<span class=\"red\">楊岳橋</span>強調，警方不應濫用「暴動」控罪，但<span class=\"red\">相信法庭有能力把關，不會成為協助警方濫用「暴動」罪打壓社會運動的工具</span>。"},{"pid":"dd07d86426f89a87a585b8a5846b5abc9c0349eb","tid":2262034,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2019a7b184f88b5b9e7a64fdf528f23c8a9da128","tid":2262034,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e00446ce53590b8b2d0e9ec1973436f7f3df52","tid":2262034,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:29:34.000Z","msg":"帶部Nokia3310出街"},{"pid":"775229198f59926db5b39c59d8dcb616ed253ecf","tid":2262034,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:25:47.000Z","msg":"乾淨手機"},{"pid":"a89f9b7094080c4968fb1c9357532ca630298a38","tid":2262034,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:27:31.000Z","msg":"屌。。。警犬D權力大到仆街"},{"pid":"8c65bcd1261fc4c5cea066711fcabefce20ec187","tid":2262034,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:27:36.000Z","msg":"即係黑狗無以色列cellabite軟件後爆唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /